---
title: Sticky Grilled Lemongrass Chicken with Nutty Rice and Bright Mango Slaw
description: Aromatic lemongrass and sweet chilli-kissed grilled chicken thighs are the highlight of this summery grill recipe! Perfectly paired with nutty rice and a bright mango slaw, what else could you ask for?
